window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Don't be Distracted. Trust the Quest. Kill your Target.</p> <p>Claire's home has burned to the ground. Displaced and plagued by nightmares, Claire can't rest as she continues her quest to eliminate every target.</p> <p>And though she gets stronger by the day, so do her targets. Her skills will be put to the limit as she does everything in her power to reach Target 75.</p> <p>More Dungeons, More Targets, Warring Factions, Broken Cities. Book 2 in this action-packed story is sure to surprise you.</p>"; 
